Syntax: holystrike <target>

Channels holy energy into a powerful weapon strike, dealing additional holy
damage to the target. Holystrike is a Warrior-line finisher skill: it
requires a valid finisher combo count before it can be activated.

Holystrike is available to Warden-class characters and their remort
descendants, particularly Paladin and Crusader who have strong holy-damage
synergies.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Requires a valid finisher combo count (combo threshold met).
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp holystrike fleche charge riposte
